<p>
<lb n="1"/><seg xml:lang="kan-Latn" rendition="class:kannada maturity:undetermined">śrīmaddākṣārāmada bhīmēsvaradēva(ra)maṁddirābhyaṁttaradoḷḷu kōmalasudī</seg>
<lb n="2" break="no"/><seg xml:lang="kan-Latn" rendition="class:kannada maturity:undetermined">padaṇḍama nīmahi pogaḍaluke nilisi(ṁ)daṁ sivarāja [*<g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g>] piridaṁdritsāhamāga</seg>
<lb n="3" break="no"/><seg xml:lang="kan-Latn" rendition="class:kannada maturity:undetermined">lu darage sivandaṇḍēśanāltiṁttu bhīmēsvarapadāṁbhōja bhaktisthitiyananudi</seg>
<lb n="4" break="no"/><seg xml:lang="kan-Latn" rendition="class:kannada maturity:undetermined">naṁ ddīpisalu tanna kīrttisphuritālaṁkkāramāśā <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> sayaṁddīpisa</seg>
<lb n="5" break="no"/><seg xml:lang="kan-Latn" rendition="class:kannada maturity:undetermined"> <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> kēṁdralakṣmīkaradīpastaṁbhamaṁ sthāpisida<unclear>no</unclear> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> saṁsayi ya</seg>
<lb n="6"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> samasta <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> śraya <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> vallabha ma
<lb n="7" break="no"/><unclear>harājā</unclear>dhirāja paramēśvara paramabhaṭṭāraka satyāśrayakulatilaka cālukyā
<lb n="8" break="no"/><unclear>bhara</unclear>ṇa śrīmattribhuvanamalladēvara vijayarājyamuttarōttarābhivri
<lb n="9" break="no"/><unclear>ddhi</unclear> pravarddhamānamācaṁdratārakaṁ cirasthāyigā śrīmaccālukyavikramasaṁ
<lb n="10" break="no"/><unclear>va</unclear>tsa 46 gu śrāhi viṣuvatsaṁkrāṁttinimittamunaṁ peggaḍa sivvaraju tama
<lb n="11" break="no"/>ku darmattamugāṁ beṭṭina Akhaṇḍa diviya 1 ṇṭaki nācaṁdrārkkamu neyi
<lb n="12"/>sariṁccuvārugā śrībhīmēsvaramahādēvara kilaramuna nāvabōla prōlaṇḍunu kāṭa
<lb n="13" break="no"/>bōla paṇḍaṇḍunu Eṟiyabōla bādaṇḍunu talarāsi nāvaya berasina bō
<lb n="14" break="no"/>lu nalluruṁ būṇṭagā Eriyabōla bādani haḍapuna kētabōla duggani va 
<lb n="15" break="no"/>samunaṁ beṭṭinā yinupaEḍlu 50 dīniki nityapaḍi golavaṁggalavāru tribhu
<lb n="16" break="no"/>vanāṁkku<unclear>śa</unclear>muna nē māna 1 likitaṁ peddanāśāri <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
